## Synopsis
Assignment of Fundamentals of Programming COMP5005

## Contents
README – readme file for Assignment
1. adventureworld.py - driver program to simulate ButtonControl.py, Patrons.py, Rides.py, Statistics.py and Terrains.py 
                       2 mode(interactive mode and batch mode) and error handling
                       after timestamp, save 'Adventureworld Statistics YYYY-mm-dd_HH:MM:SS.png' image

2. Patrons.py
    Patrons() - manage the movement, state, and position of Patron walking around an theme park

3. Rides.py
    FerrisWheel(Rides) - FerrisWheel class set direction and movement, manage break, riding and queue
    DropTower(Rides) - DropTower class set direction and movement, manage break, riding and queue
    Hurricane(Rides) - Hurricane class set direction and movement, manage break, riding and queue
    PirateShip(Rides) - PirateShip class set direction and movement, manage break, riding and queue

4. Terrains.py
    Terrains() - plot map(sky, ground, sun, moon, and cloud)
    Pond() - plot barrier(pond)
    
5. Statistics.py 
    LinePlot(Statistics) - plot line graph about 'Each Ride Profits Per Time Stamp'
    TablePlot(Statistics) - plot table about '# Operations', '# Patrons', 'Price', '# Profit'
    ScatterPlot(Statistics) - Plot scatter graph about 'Patrons movement'

6. BottonControl.py
    SpeedControl() - manages the temporal speed of the simulation loop
    WeatherControl() - manages the rain visualization using animation loop on a matplotlib Axes object


7. map_dawn.csv - time of day(dawn) + sun(#FF6666) + ground(#8cc751)
   map_morning.csv - time of day(morning) + sun(#FFFF99) + ground(lightgreen)
   map_sunset.csv - time of day(sunset) + sun(orangered) + ground(#8cc751)
   map_midnight.csv - time of day(midnight) + moon(gold) + ground(olivedrab)
   map_mix.csv - whole day(dawn + morning + sunset + midnight)

8. param1.csv - batch mode parameters file(set normal values)
   param2.csv - batch mode parameters file(set some unnormal values)
   param3.csv - batch mode parameters file(set some normal + unnormal + null values)
   
9. scenario_param1.csv - batch mode scenario parameters file(set 200 timestamp, 10 patrons, 2 rides)
   scenario_param2.csv - batch mode scenario parameters file(set 200 timestamp, 30 patrons, 3 rides) 
   scenario_param3.csv - batch mode scenario parameters file(set 200 timestamp, 40 patrons, 4 rides)  
    
    
## Dependencies
matplotlib, scipy, numpy, random, queue, names, csv, pandas, and datetime

## Version information
07/10/2025 - initial version of Assignment programs

